<i>noun</i>: 웃음거리 [우슴꺼리], 능멸 [능멸], 경멸 [경멸] <i>verb</i>: 능멸하다 [능멸하다] <br>
<ul style="list-style-type:square">
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt>웃음거리 [우슴꺼리]</dt><br>
<dd>1. laughing stock; scorn; derision; ridicule</dd><br>
<dd>남에게 비웃음을 당할 만한 일.</dd><br>
<dd>The behavior that deserves to be laughed at by others.</dd><br>
<dd>2. laughing stock; fool</dd><br>
<dd>남에게 비웃음을 당할 만한 사람.</dd><br>
<dd>A person who deserves to be laughed at by others.</dd><br>
<dt>능멸 [능멸]</dt><br>
<dd>contempt; disdain; scorn</dd><br>
<dd>남을 하찮게 여겨 깔봄.</dd><br>
<dd>Belittling and looking down on someone.</dd><br>
<dt>경멸 [경멸]</dt><br>
<dd>contempt; scorn</dd><br>
<dd>매우 싫어하거나 무시하는 듯한 태도로 낮추어 봄.</dd><br>
<dd>Looking down on someone with an attitude of extreme dislike or disdain.</dd><br>
</li>
<li><i>verb</i><br>
<dt>능멸하다 [능멸하다]</dt><br>
<dd>scorn; disdain</dd><br>
<dd>남을 하찮게 여겨 깔보다.</dd><br>
<dd>To look down on another person and belittle him/her.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>